column2: hey almond list wall street journal articles with update times equal to this year
their link of my instagram pictures
alert me wherever new york times clauses published this week change and the update time is earlier than DURATION_0 after last year with the text in real life
column3: monitor ( @com.nytimes . get_front_page ( ) filter updated <= $end_of ( year ) + DURATION_0 && updated >= $start_of ( week ) ) => @org.thingpedia.builtin.thingengine.builtin . say ( message = " in real life " ) ;

column2: find my dropbox files in alphabetical order having bigger size than NUMBER_0 byte
column3: @com.dropbox . list_folder ( order_by = enum name_increasing ) filter file_size >= NUMBER_0 byte ;

column2: when it stops snowing in LOCATION_0 tell me my google drive files smaller than NUMBER_0 gigabytes
column3: monitor ( @org.thingpedia.weather . current ( location = LOCATION_0 ) ) filter ! ( status == enum snowy ) => @com.google.drive . list_drive_files ( ) filter file_size <= NUMBER_0 GB ;

column2: number the list of all memes with name equivalent to pepperidge farm remembers
column3: @com.imgflip . list ( ) filter name == " pepperidge farm remembers " ;

column2: i want a photo positioned on facebook
hey almond what are a price estimate for uber from here to LOCATION_0 having high estimates lower than CURRENCY_0 ?
column3: @com.uber . price_estimate ( end = LOCATION_0 , start = $location . current_location ) filter high_estimate <= CURRENCY_0 ;

column2: give me posts in the washington post capital weather gang blog when somebody sends me a direct message
column3: monitor ( @com.twitter . direct_messages ( ) ) => @com.washingtonpost . get_blog_post ( section = enum capital_weather_gang ) ;

column2: if the corporation name is lemaitre vascular inc. let me know of updates in novadaq technologies inc stocks
column3: monitor ( @com.yahoo.finance . get_stock_quote ( stock_id = null ^^tt:stock_id ( " novadaq technologies inc " ) ) ) filter company_name == " lemaitre vascular inc. " ;

column2: auto share my new dropbox files that changed most recently on linkedin
column3: monitor ( @com.dropbox . list_folder ( order_by = enum modified_time_decreasing ) ) => @com.linkedin . share ( status = $result ) ;

column2: show the message real time in case of changes in articles in the washington post in section business with headlines equal to okcupid attack mozilla over gay rights
column3: monitor ( @com.washingtonpost . get_article ( section = enum business ) filter title == " okcupid attack mozilla over gay rights " ) => @org.thingpedia.builtin.thingengine.builtin . say ( message = " real time " ) ;
